						               													<description>Zirkus Leo brings Leo the Lion and his friends into the ring where players will experience many turbulent events. In this speedy card game, players try to play the cards from their hand as quickly as possible, and to carry out all actions quickly and correctly, so as not to receive any more cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players must concentrate, because all actions shown on the cards are carried out at the same time. As a general rule, whoever is the last to perform the action receives all the cards in the ring.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Pay attention, as the illustrations on the cards provide assistance. However, since there are a total of 14 different action cards, it is not always easy to perform the correct action immediately. Whoever has the fewest cards at the end wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
